Titolo: Battle Dex

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: Battle Dex was an online, turn-based strategy game featuring collectible cards inspired by Advance Wars and Magic: The Gathering. An open beta of the game ran from April to November 2010 and the game was publicly released on November 7, 2010.The game was created by Bandera Games, an Austin, TX-based game development studio founded by veterans of such companies as NCsoft, Realm Interactive, and Vigil Games. The game was free-to-play with the option for users to purchase single-player missions, decks of cards, and points.
Battle Dex is not operational since 2016.

Genere: Turn-based strategy

Valutazione: N/A
